(json 25 (content "<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;DataUnion.app is building DataUnions-as-a-service for AI ready data and co-owned insights. As we are expanding the number of DataUnions building with our technology stack, we are looking to integrate with AI marketplaces to monetise the AI created on top of their data. SingularityNET is THE decentralised AI marketplace so an integration is a must.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:897,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">DataUnion.app is building DataUnions-as-a-service for AI ready data and co-owned insights. As we are expanding the number of DataUnions building with our technology stack, we are looking to integrate with AI marketplaces to monetize the AI created on top of their data. SingularityNET is THE decentralized AI marketplace so integration is a must.</span></p>"))
