(json 28 (title "GPT for sNET &amp; Cardano"))
(json 28 (content "<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;This proposal outlines the integration of open.ai - ChatGPT with Discord to improve the accuracy and relevance of the model's responses on Cardano and SingularityNET-related topics. By using Discord chats to train the model, we aim to create a ChatGPT that is a mastermind on all things related to Cardano and SingularityNET, making it a valuable resource for the community.\&quot;&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:897,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">This proposal outlines the integration of open.ai - ChatGPT with Discord to improve the accuracy and relevance of the model's responses on Cardano and SingularityNET-related topics. By using Discord chats to train the model, we aim to create a ChatGPT that is a mastermind on all things related to Cardano and SingularityNET, making it a valuable resource for the community."</span></p>"))
