(json 31 (title "Computer vision based farm status and recommender system"))
(json 31 (content "<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Most ML/AI solutions developed for analyzing farms only end up being used by large farms who have the ability to purchase large technologies that are needed to operate these models.\nOur solution makes farm status and recommendation system easily available to all farmers, developers etc who needs it without the need for sophisticated tools.\n&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:897,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">Most ML/AI solutions developed for analyzing farms only end up being used by large farms who have the ability to purchase large technologies that are needed to operate these models.<br />
Our solution makes farm status and recommendation system easily available to all farmers, developers etc who needs it without the need for sophisticated tools.<br />
</span></p>"))
