(json 41 (content "<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;We will build a SingularityNet service that will make it easier for developers to use ready-made popular open-source AI libraries in their projects. The service will provide clean, documented APIs and full virtualization (using Docker) of these AIs, allowing developers to easily access and integrate them in their apps.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:897,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}">We will build a SingularityNet service that will make it easier for developers to use ready-made popular open-source AI libraries in their projects. The service will provide clean, documented APIs and full virtualization (using Docker) of these AIs, allowing developers to easily access and integrate them in their apps.</span></p>"))
