(json 42 (title "Composable AI from Appstorm@Zero2AI"))
(json 42 (content "<p>Zero2AI proposes a project with a budget of $78,000 (engineering costs), $30,000 (API/cloud cost), and $12,000 (on-boarding cost) to develop a framework that integrates SingularityNET (SNET) services as building blocks into their Appstorm AI app creation platform. Appstorm enables non-technical users to create AI applications with ease. By integrating SNET services, they aim to democratize access to AI services and foster an explosion of AI app creation. The project milestones include design and prototype, implementation of SNET services, QA and production readiness, payment integration, private stand-alone app prototype, and more. The team emphasizes low implementation risks and plans to launch a community token in Q1 2024 to incentivize creators and consumers while promoting SNET services. Open-sourcing is also planned in the near future. The team includes experienced professionals in AI, Web3, and cloud infrastructure.</p>"))
(json 42 (link "https://deepfunding.ai/proposal/composable-ai-from-appstormzero2ai/"))
