(json 43 (title "AI career guide"))
(json 43 (content "<p>AI Career Counselling aims to use AI to identify personality traits and career aspects to assist human career counsellors rather than replace them. They are seeking $300 in funding to reduce confusion for clients and counsellors while providing the best career advice. The project involves creating plans and guiding clients in the right direction, acting as a bridge between clients and career counsellors. Their marketing strategy focuses on making career and counsellor selection faster and easier. The project milestones include website development and research, with a breakdown of costs. The risks involve acquiring clients and counsellors, which they plan to mitigate through cost reduction and in-house organic marketing, with a voluntary revenue goal of $5.</p>"))
