(json 47 (title "Generative AI Decision Making Advisor: Greening Power Generation for Budgets and the Environment"))
(json 47 (content "<p>MLBoost's objective is to create decision-making advisor software driven by generative technologies, initially targeting power plant operations to improve efficiency and reduce energy consumption. This Proof of Concept (POC) serves as a critical demonstration of their technology's potential. Current power plant operations are hindered by slow mathematical optimization methods, resulting in suboptimal performance and increased emissions. MLBoost's POC phase involves sourcing Power Plant Digital Models (PDMs) and comparing generative optimization methods with conventional approaches. The success of this POC will lay the foundation for future software development on the SingularityNet platform, integrating forecasting services like SYBIL for smarter decision-making. The marketing strategy centers on showcasing the solution's superiority to power plant operators, utility companies, and sustainability agencies through case studies and quantifiable metrics.</p>"))
(json 47 (link "https://deepfunding.ai/proposal/generative-ai-decision-making-advisor-greening-power-generation-for-budgets-and-the-environment/"))
