(json 51 (title "SingularityNet Marketplace ChatGPT plugin"))
(json 51 (content "<p>Arbiteria proposes creating a ChatGPT plugin to address the lack of information about decentralized AI and the SingularityNet platform. This plugin, funded with $39,000, will provide ChatGPTPlus users with responses related to decentralized AI queries, including information about SingularityNet AI Marketplace listings and the benefits of decentralized AI.</p>
<p>The project aims to raise awareness among both technical and non-technical users in the decentralized AI space. It also serves as a discreet marketing asset, potentially increasing user traffic to the SingularityNet platform and transactions in the SNET marketplace.</p>
<p>The project is divided into four milestones, including building the plugin, incorporating SNET marketplace apps, surfacing specific SNET information, and providing public Beta support. Mitigation strategies are in place in case key stakeholders do not reach a consensus on the information to surface.</p>
<p>The project is open source and may involve voluntary revenue sharing with SNET/Deep Funding for larger or high-risk projects.</p>"))
