(json 57 (title "Socious: AI-Based Job Matching for Social Good"))
(json 57 (content "<p>Socious is addressing the gap between young people's desire to use their skills for social and environmental good and their ability to find such jobs. Their innovative AI solution curates purpose-driven jobs and matches them with individuals based on their passion and skills. By considering social causes, they aim to create a more meaningful match between talent and impact jobs. Socious operates as a Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO) and aligns with SingularityNET's vision of decentralized AI for a beneficial Singularity. They have achieved significant traction, listing over 70,000 impact jobs, registering 22,000 impact organizations, and attracting over 5,000 purpose-driven professionals. Their project milestones include solution architecture, completing the Impact Job Detector and Matching Engine, SingularityNET platform onboarding, and marketing efforts. Socious plans to launch a utility token, THANK, and allocate 10% of the pre-seed round allocation to SNET/Deep Funding to support their mission further.</p>"))
