(json 58 (title "NIM Framework | Framework for integrating AI services in Singularity Marketplace and bots in Matrix | Matrix Messenger"))
(json 58 (content "<p>NIM (Native Intelligence Messenger) seeks to streamline communication by integrating AI services directly into messaging platforms. NIM's framework, compatible with the decentralized Matrix protocol, enables users to seamlessly access various AI bots within a single messenger app. This revolutionary approach eliminates the need for users to switch between applications, enhancing efficiency and productivity. Key features include a unified, user-friendly interface, personalized interactions based on user history, natural and interactive dialogues with AI bots, stringent data security measures, continuous product development, and interoperability for creating unique AI service pipelines. With a budget of $180-210k, NIM plans to achieve these milestones and make AI integration into messaging a game-changer. Additionally, they seek input from AI experts, marketers, and product analysts and aim to hire a frontend developer to expedite development. The framework will be open source, while the messenger itself will be a closed team project.</p>"))
