(json 60 (title "AI-Enabled full value audit and dashboard for sustainable exponential organisational growth"))
(json 60 (content "<p style="text-align: left;">Edify CoLabs proposes an AI-enabled full value audit platform to help organizations adapt to rapid, disruptive change. Traditional management practices struggle to keep pace with technological advancements, leaving businesses unable to measure their full value, particularly intangible assets. This solution automates the full value audit methodology and guides organizations through the process. It aims to address the challenges of valuing assets, understanding their impact, and dealing with exponential growth. EdifyAI's target market includes a wide range of organizations, from private enterprises to public entities, both on-chain and off-chain, new and established, across various sectors and geographies. Their marketing strategy focuses on social media, academic networks, and special interest communities to drive engagement and adoption.</p>"))
