(json 63 (title "MeAI tool for healthcare system"))
(json 63 (content "<p>Cardano2vn.io Company seeks $39,000 in funding to develop the Medical AI (MeAI) tool, which aims to address the early diagnosis of stomach diseases, particularly cancer, using endoscopic images. Stomach cancer is a significant health concern globally and in Vietnam, with a growing number of cases, especially among younger individuals. The tool utilizes AI to analyze endoscopic images, identifying abnormalities such as polyps, gastritis, and cancerous lesions, providing users with advice on whether they should undergo further examinations.</p>
<p>The project involves several key steps, including data collection, AI model development, training, deployment, and continuous improvement based on user data. MeAI offers a primary API function for users to upload medical images, obtain diagnostic results, and significantly reduce waiting times while ensuring high accuracy.</p>
<p>Potential risks include data collection challenges, data accuracy, and model effectiveness, which the project aims to mitigate through careful planning, expert collaboration, and rigorous experimentation. The voluntary revenue sources for MeAI include charge-based requests and in-app advertising, making the tool sustainable in the long run.</p>"))
