(json 66 (title "Funding Funnels:  An AI Event with Funding Pathway for Young Innovators"))
(json 66 (content "<p>STAR HIVE INITIATIVE plans to organize "Funding Funnels," a 3-day event aiming to bring together over 2,000 young tech enthusiasts and innovators from around the world. This event, taking place both physically and virtually, will focus on integrating participants into the SingularityNET (SNET) ecosystem through workshops, seminars, networking sessions, and an innovation pitch-a-thon and intellect fair exhibition competition. The top-performing innovators will receive rewards in AGIX tokens, while others will be mentored to submit their ideas and innovations to the next deep funding rounds.</p>
<p>The requested funding amount is $5,000. The problem being addressed is the lack of proper infrastructure and collaborative systems for young innovators to access resources and connect with industry experts. Many are unaware of the opportunities within the SNET and deep funding ecosystem.</p>
<p>The project milestones include event conceptualization, logistical engagements, organizing the intellect fair and innovation pitch-a-thon, workshop implementation, skill-building, mentorship, post-conference evaluation, and integration into deep funding. Mitigation strategies are outlined for potential risks, including financial, technical, health and safety, speaker cancellations, low attendance, intellectual property, vendor issues, logistics challenges, weather or natural disasters, and cybersecurity risks.</p>
<p>The initiative aims to foster a dynamic and inclusive tech ecosystem that supports young innovators and drives progress globally.</p>"))
