(json 67 (title "DeepFunding Academy &#8211; Phase 1: Genesis"))
(json 67 (content "<p>DeepFunding Academy aims to secure $35,665 USD in AGIX funding to establish an educational initiative powered by the Andamio learning management system (LMS). This initiative is designed to support the education and onboarding of community members within the DeepFunding ecosystem, acquainting them with roles like proposers, reviewers, voters, and emerging functions.</p>
<p>The initial phase, called Genesis, focuses on establishing core team operations, implementing the LMS, training educators, developing educational content, and hosting live online workshops. The goal is to enhance community engagement, elevate contribution quality, and distribute key DeepFunding operations to the community, reducing reliance on the core team.</p>
<p>Future phases will explore AI and machine learning applications within the DeepFunding Academy. The proposal underscores a step-by-step approach that aligns with DeepFunding's evolution and aims to support the broader objectives of SingularityNET and Cardano.</p>
<p>In summary, DeepFunding Academy seeks funding to create an extensive educational framework, promoting community involvement and contributing to the growth and sustainability of the Cardano ecosystem.</p>"))
