(json 70 (title "Architectural Design for Uncertain Knowledge Graphs"))
(json 70 (content "<p>Photrek's proposal for the "Tools for Knowledge Graphs and LLMs Integration" project outlines their objective to address uncertainty in knowledge graphs (KGs) and their integration with large language models (LLMs). They aim to embed a model of uncertainty into KGs at both micro and macro levels. At the micro level, Photrek will introduce confidence measures for each fact in KGs, enhancing traditional probability-based models with upper and lower bounds based on relative risk aversion. This approach allows for a wider range of uncertainty computations in KG inference.</p>
<p>At the macro level, they will design a methodology for managing short-term and long-term memory in KGs using generative AI methods. This involves monitoring and updating short-term and long-term memory to facilitate effective KG inference while avoiding overconfidence and errors.</p>
<p>Photrek plans to collaborate closely with SingularityNET's KG and LLM teams to determine priorities, with the higher priority item resulting in a detailed architectural design documented in a research report. The ultimate goal is to improve fact-checking and knowledge graph updates.</p>"))
(json 70 (link "https://deepfunding.ai/proposal/architectural-design-for-uncertain-knowledge-graphs/"))
(json 70 (feature_image "https://deepfunding.ai/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3.jpg"))
(json 70 (requested_amount "$40,000"))
(json 70 (awarded_amount "$40,000"))
(json 70 (is_awarded True))
(json 70 (created_at "2023-09-02 20:51:46"))
