(json 84 (title "Building SNET AI Community across China"))
(json 84 (content "<p>This proposal aims to enhance awareness of the SingularityNET (SNET) AI ecosystem in China. With a funding amount of $8,500, the initiative seeks to address the limited knowledge of SNET within the Chinese community despite widespread AI adoption. To introduce SNET to the Chinese audience, the project plans to conduct offline workshops in four different cities across China. These workshops will cover SNET's introduction, ecosystem overview, AI marketplace, AGIX staking, Deep Funding introduction, and more. About 50 attendees are expected per event, and incentives like free drinks, marketing materials, and gifts for active participation will be provided. The project's milestones and cost breakdown are outlined in a spreadsheet. The team, led by crypto enthusiasts like cryptobeijing, aims to build a local SNET AI community in China by focusing on AI-related topics due to China's cautious stance on crypto.</p>"))
