(json 88 (content "<p>AI Song Starter is a revolutionary tool designed to streamline music production by generating custom loops and stems based on text prompts or audio inputs. This tool helps musicians overcome writer's block, save time, and enhance creativity. By integrating with SingularityNET AI Marketplace, it democratizes access to advanced music production tools, fostering creativity and innovation across the music industry. This initiative supports over 60 million musicians worldwide, driving broader adoption and engagement within the SingularityNET ecosystem.</p>"))
