(json 96 (title "AGIX/ASI Payment Gateway for SaaS products"))
(json 96 (content "<p>The AGIX/ASI Payment Gateway aims to provide a simple and secure payment solution for SaaS product developers to collect payment in AGIX/ASI. This ideation phase will focus on researching, assessing feasibility, and designing the architecture for a payment gateway that supports AGIX and ASI tokens. By addressing the community's need for a reliable payment infrastructure, this project will facilitate the monetization of SingularityNETs tokens, expanding the utility and infrastructure possibilities.</p>"))
