(json 101 (title "SingularityNET Asian Community"))
(json 101 (content "<p>This project focuses on closing the gap in localized content and community engagement for SingularityNET across key Asian markets, including China, Hong Kong, Taiwan, Singapore, and Malaysia. Despite existing KOL and media exposure, our initiative aims to enhance awareness and foster collaborations by promoting SingularityNET, DeepFunding, and the broader AI platform through comprehensive channel exposure on platforms like Instagram, YouTube, Twitter, and community forums. The main objectives are to amplify awareness, create tailored regional content, and actively engage AI talent, thereby expanding SingularityNET's influence and participation in these crucial markets.</p>"))
