(json 102 (title "Next Trend LAB: Exploring Decentralized AI for IoT"))
(json 102 (content "<p>Next Trend LAB aims to revolutionize SingularityNET by researching the integration of decentralized AI algorithms with IoT. This exploration promises to enhance automation, predictive maintenance, and decision-making in smart environments. By bridging AI with IoT, we'll unlock innovative solutions, driving the adoption of AGIX tokens and expanding SingularityNET's ecosystem.</p>"))
