(json 103 (title "Bridging SNET AI Services To Unity Apps"))
(json 103 (content "<p>Our project aims to bridge the SingularityNET AI Marketplace with the Unity ecosystem, enabling seamless integration of AI services into 3D/VR/AR applications. We will develop Unity scripts and tools to simplify the discovery and interaction with AI services, specifically integrating the ‘Song Splitter’ and ‘AI Synthesizer’ into our 3D Music Studio app. This will unlock vast potential in gaming, education, and digital entertainment, providing over 2 million Unity developers access to powerful AI tools, fostering innovation, and expanding the SingularityNET ecosystem.</p>"))
