(json 104 (title "How to SingularityNet? (Course)"))
(json 104 (content "<p>Our proposed project focuses on expanding SingularityNet's adoption by developing an educational course aimed at teaching users to effectively utilize its AI services. This course, designed for users across all sectors, will include comprehensive tutorials on platform navigation, service selection, and integration into business activities. Delivered via interactive modules on Andamio, live workshops, and hands-on projects, the course aims to demystify AI service integration, boosting user engagement. Participants completing the course will receive NFT and AGIX rewards. The project's impact will be measured through metrics like user engagement rates and feedback, guiding further improvements.</p>"))
(json 104 (link "https://deepfunding.ai/proposal/how-to-singularitynet/"))
