(json 105 (title "Real-Time Multi-Lingual SNET Transcription Tool"))
(json 105 (content "<p style="padding-left: 40px;">It's a global world, and interconnection and collaboration have become the trend of the day. Knowledge of English seems to be the passport to this interconnected world, unfortunately, more than 50% of the world is not English natives and this hinders the efficiency of global collaborations. This is a global problem, many organizations, companies, ecosystems, DAOs, etc are facing this challenge. My recent research under the Research and Development Guild revealed that this problem is endemic even in the SNet, Deepfunding, and ambassadorial community as well, this necessitates a tool that will help our community but in extension, every other organization and ecosystem needing a similar tool.</p>"))
