(json 108 (title "SingularityNET Africa Community"))
(json 108 (content "<p>This project seeks to expand the reach and impact of SingularityNET into Africa, especially given the latent potential of Africa in contributing to the tech and entrepreneurship ecosystems. We aim to amplify awareness and engagement in leading countries like Nigeria, Egypt, Rwanda, South Africa and Cote d'Ivoire. Through partnerships, community engagement initiatives, hackathons/conferences, townhalls and university events, we'll expand the SingularityNET ecosystem and promote the ambassador program as well as DeepFunding's benefits, aiming for increased participation in the SingularityNET ecosystem in general.</p>"))
