(json 122 (title "Jam Galaxy Roblox Game – Bringing SNet to 70M Daily Users"))
(json 122 (content "<p>"Galactic Jam Machine," developed by MetaHug for Roblox, is an immersive musical adventure blending creativity, community, and space exploration. Targeting teens and adults, it allows players to compose music using cosmic-themed blocks and AI-driven creatures. The game emphasizes community sharing, offering a Galactic Gallery for showcasing compositions. With a 16-18 week development timeline and a $50,000 budget, its monetization strategy includes selling unique in-game items and premium access. This project stands out as a creative platform for musical expression in a dynamic 3D environment.</p>"))
(json 122 (link "https://deepfunding.ai/proposal/galactic-jam-machine-on-roblox/"))
